data.description: So much space! Move right in to this split foyer home in established neighborhood (which has no HOA!). Beamed ceilings in upstairs living area, along with dining room and updated kitchen. Kitchen is bright and airy- white Shaker cabinets, quartz countertops and stainless steel appliances. A door in the dining area leads to a covered deck that overlooks an expansive fenced backyard. You'll find the master bedroom & bathroom and 2 additional bedrooms and 1 full bathroom on this same level. Head downstairs and you'll find the laundry closet and another large living area, complete with a wood-burning fireplace. Continuing the tour downstairs, you'll find another full bathroom, a 4th bedroom with access to the lower portion of the large backyard and a flex space with white built-in upper and lower cabinets and solid surface countertops- perfect for a long-term guest, craft room, man-cave, etc. The possibilities are endless and the space just keeps going and going. Come see this gem for yourself! House is sold AS IS.
